{"parse":{"title":"Herpes Viruses Association","pageid":48204902,"revid":846879728,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The Herpes Association (now the <b>Herpes Viruses Association</b>) was started in 1982.  It is a <a href=\"/wiki/Herpes_support_groups\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Herpes support groups\">support group</a> for people with <a href=\"/wiki/Herpes_simplex_virus\" title=\"Herpes simplex virus\">Herpes simplex virus</a>. It conducts information campaigns and attempts to reduce the stigma associated with sexually transmitted diseases.\n</p><p>It became a registered charity with a Dept of Health grant in 1985.  The charity started as a string of local group meetings before acquiring an office and a national spread.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is widely referred to as a source of help for patients who are anxious about the conditions,<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> primarily genital herpes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Association campaigns against the transmission of herpes being treated as a criminal offence. It supported David Golding who was convicted and imprisoned for infecting a woman with genital herpes in 2011.<sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> Their spokesman said the sentence for causing grievous bodily harm was \u2018outrageous\u2019 and compared it to prosecuting children for \u2018giving their friends chicken pox\u2019,<sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> or passing on a cold sore.<sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It supported the campaign to keep the sexual health services of the <a href=\"/wiki/Countess_of_Chester_Hospital_NHS_Foundation_Trust\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Countess of Chester Hospital NHS Foundation Trust\">Countess of Chester Hospital NHS Foundation Trust</a> in 2014.<sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>It carried out a double-blind trial of liquorice lip balm on forty people in 2014  and found that it reduced the severity of symptoms in most subjects.<sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup>  Marian Nicholson, the Director of the Association, is frequently quoted in relation to research into the development of remedies.<sup id=\"cite_ref-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-11\">&#91;11&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Dr <a href=\"/wiki/Phil_Hammond_(comedian)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Phil Hammond (comedian)\">Phil Hammond (comedian)</a> is the president of the association.  Between 1993 and 2002 <a href=\"/wiki/Clare_Rayner\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Clare Rayner\">Clare Rayner</a> was one of its patrons.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Herpes_Viruses_Association&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"reflist\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.herpessupport.org/2014/04/uk-herpes-dating-sites-and-herpes.html\">\"UK Herpes Support Groups\"</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=UK+Herpes+Support+Groups&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.herpessupport.org%2F2014%2F04%2Fuk-herpes-dating-sites-and-herpes.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerpes+Viruses+Association\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20150113155048/http://www.hva.org.uk/aboutus.html\">\"The Herpes Viruses Association\"</a>. Archived from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hva.org.uk/aboutus.html\">the original</a> on 2015-01-13.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=The+Herpes+Viruses+Association&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hva.org.uk%2Faboutus.html&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerpes+Viruses+Association\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nursinginpractice.com/article/gynaecological-infections\">\"Gynaecological infections\"</a>. Nursing in practice. 20 May 2015<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Gynaecological+infections&amp;rft.date=2015-05-20&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nursinginpractice.com%2Farticle%2Fgynaecological-infections&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerpes+Viruses+Association\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/Genital-herpes/Pages/Introduction.aspx\">\"Genital herpes\"</a>. <i>NHS Choices</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=NHS+Choices&amp;rft.atitle=Genital+herpes&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nhs.uk%2Fconditions%2FGenital-herpes%2FPages%2FIntroduction.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerpes+Viruses+Association\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-northamptonshire-27330273\">\"David Golding: Court criticised over herpes infector ruling\"</a>. BBC News. 8 May 2014<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">13 October</span> 2015</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=David+Golding%3A+Court+criticised+over+herpes+infector+ruling&amp;rft.date=2014-05-08&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk-england-northamptonshire-27330273&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AHerpes+Viruses+Association\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"referen